news_header: OP Group's operating profit increased to EUR 720 million in July-September.
news_text: OP Group’s operating profit for July-September increased to EUR 720 million from EUR 584 million last year. Interest rates fell by 1.6% to EUR 712 million due to declining market interest rates. Timo Ritakallio noted that the operating profit was excellent in the third quarter, and the recovery in the Finnish economy appears to be continuing, particularly due to improvements in domestic markets.
